Subject: Re: [T2] Re: microbus

While any year tank will fit into the space, there are other differences besides the outlets.  The FI tanks have a different sender that is not interchangeable with the non-FI tanks.  If you get a non-FI tank, be sure to get the correct sender to go with it.

-David
